  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.poster.avif?t=1698681062\" width=600 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.webm?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.mp4?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Loop is a fun puzzle game that will exercise your brain! Get lost in a world of grid systems and colorful stones. Your goal is to move the stones up, down, left, and right to place them in their correct positions. But be careful, each stone moves at the same time, and if there is no grid cell available in the direction it needs to go, it will be teleported to the opposite side of the grid!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.poster.avif?t=1698681062\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.webm?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.mp4?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With its minimal graphics and enjoyable music, Loop provides a calming atmosphere that will envelop you. If you want to exercise your brain and experience a new puzzle game, Loop is just for you!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.poster.avif?t=1698681062\" width=600 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.webm?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/8919ba5587d09f32d809b3960fe6e76d.mp4?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Loop is a fun puzzle game that will exercise your brain! Get lost in a world of grid systems and colorful stones. Your goal is to move the stones up, down, left, and right to place them in their correct positions. But be careful, each stone moves at the same time, and if there is no grid cell available in the direction it needs to go, it will be teleported to the opposite side of the grid!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.poster.avif?t=1698681062\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.webm?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346490/extras/861848837ee7135586e5f23af98cdba2.mp4?t=1698681062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With its minimal graphics and enjoyable music, Loop provides a calming atmosphere that will envelop you. If you want to exercise your brain and experience a new puzzle game, Loop is just for you!",
